{
  "stem": "6845.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So, as a good-- as a proof of it, when I got home a year later, I gained 40 pounds.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I shouldn't forget it that the first sentence from my mother was, my child, I sent you to acquire the French language.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But what I see, you certainly acquired lots of pounds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So she was very unhappy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she was right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I did learn the French language quite easily.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I really liked it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We, we did things which we would have never done and had skating lessons with ex-Russian aristocrats who were during the White Russian times.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they were now in bad financial shape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And everybody had a title of some kind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was learning how to dance on the ice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Well, anyway.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was nice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I could have lived without it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I did make a resolution-- if I ever would have a child, I would never send to a all-girls finishing school because it really could finish you up.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then one day, we went out to Holland on a-- for a-- the tulip season, to observe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I said, gee, tulip season.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Hmm, it might rain.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I remembered that I just had the brand-new, red plastic coat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We just came out in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And my mother bought it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I had a little red beret, mini-beret, made for it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Anyway, I was all dressed up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we went to-- by train to Holland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it was gorgeous and really, a beautiful experience, those flowers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Of course I said, gee, tomorrow, I'm going to visit my relatives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That should be nice to buy some flowers for them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I bought a big bouquet of red tulips.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And here I was, going now home.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
